-DevPulse-
A collaborative issue tracker for software teams to report bugs and suggest features.

Live URL: https://assaignment-2-level-2.vercel.app

Tech Stack
Node.js, TypeScript, Express.js, PostgreSQL, JWT, bcrypt


.env file
PORT=5000
