JWT_SECRATE=1b115fe94dc29b37771f5fea8022a10d3482d1be5e6ba86bc9c71d3b42b37f0d


-API ENDPOINTS- 
METHOD - POST-  /api/auth/signup - public
METHOD - POST-  /api/auth/login - public
METHOD - POST-  /api/issues - Authenticated
METHOD - GET -  /api/issues - public
METHOD - GET -  /api/issues/:id - public
METHOD - PATCH - /api/issues/:id - Authenticated
METHOD - DELETE - /api/issues:id - Maintainer only




Database Schema
users: id, name, email, password, role (contributor / maintainer), created_at, updated_at
issues: id, title, description, type (bug / feature_request), status (open / in_progress / resolved), reporter_id, created_at, updated_at